{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-item-js","path":"/projects/apollo-express-kontent-boilerplate","result":{"data":{"kontentItemProject":{"system":{"id":"0887625d-eb03-583f-9fd6-9eb9ab204e38"},"elements":{"title":{"value":"Apollo Express Kontent boilerplate"},"release_date":{"value":"2018-12-12T00:00:00Z"},"source_code_url":{"value":"https://github.com/Kentico/kontent-boilerplate-express-apollo"},"live_url":{"value":"https://kontent-boilerplate-apollo.herokuapp.com"},"summary":{"value":"<p>This boilerplate showcasing how to combine the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/\">Node.js</a>&nbsp;web server <a href=\"https://expressjs.com/\">Express.js</a>&nbsp;with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graphql.org/\">GraphQL</a>. The server converts the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.kontent.ai/reference/kentico-kontent-apis-overview\">Kentico Kontent Delivery REST API</a>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graphql.org/\">GraphQL</a>&nbsp;using the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.apollographql.com/\">Apollo framework</a>&nbsp;and then renders the output using the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pugjs.org/\">Pug view engine</a>.</p>"},"image":{"value":[{"url":"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/6aec6c2a-3010-01c9-8295-4d988333f15d/bd3421f9-ef53-48d7-9d61-eab2eddd8e42/schema.png","width":1914,"height":966,"description":null}]},"content":{"value":"<p>Boilerplate is combining <a href=\"https://expressjs.com\">Express.js</a> web server with <a href=\"https://www.apollographql.com\">Apollo framework</a> middleware to provide a GraphQL API wrapper around the REST API by headless CMS Kentico Kontent.</p>\n<figure data-asset-id=\"2ba687ee-fe8a-5d73-88a7-da90e96e527c\" data-image-id=\"2ba687ee-fe8a-5d73-88a7-da90e96e527c\"><img src=\"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/6aec6c2a-3010-01c9-8295-4d988333f15d/bd3421f9-ef53-48d7-9d61-eab2eddd8e42/schema.png\" data-asset-id=\"2ba687ee-fe8a-5d73-88a7-da90e96e527c\" data-image-id=\"2ba687ee-fe8a-5d73-88a7-da90e96e527c\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n<p>GraphQL schema is automatically generated using the<a href=\"https://github.com/Kentico/kontent-schema-generator-graphql\"> Kontent Schema generator tool</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>To showcase using the Apollo GraphQL client, the boilerplate is loading the last three articles stored in headless CMS and using <a href=\"https://pugjs.org\">Pug view engine</a> to construct the view of this simple listing.</p>\n<figure data-asset-id=\"15dcba0f-0972-5358-8528-3811fd8ff5fe\" data-image-id=\"15dcba0f-0972-5358-8528-3811fd8ff5fe\"><img src=\"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/6aec6c2a-3010-01c9-8295-4d988333f15d/aaf6f5d7-e73a-4fba-8728-c5776797b9be/template_thumbnail.png\" data-asset-id=\"15dcba0f-0972-5358-8528-3811fd8ff5fe\" data-image-id=\"15dcba0f-0972-5358-8528-3811fd8ff5fe\" alt=\"\"></figure>","modular_content":[],"images":[{"image_id":"2ba687ee-fe8a-5d73-88a7-da90e96e527c","url":"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/6aec6c2a-3010-01c9-8295-4d988333f15d/bd3421f9-ef53-48d7-9d61-eab2eddd8e42/schema.png","width":1914,"height":966,"description":null},{"image_id":"15dcba0f-0972-5358-8528-3811fd8ff5fe","url":"https://assets-eu-01.kc-usercontent.com:443/6aec6c2a-3010-01c9-8295-4d988333f15d/aaf6f5d7-e73a-4fba-8728-c5776797b9be/template_thumbnail.png","width":821,"height":916,"description":null}]}}}},"pageContext":{"language":"en-US","codename":"apollo_express_boilerplate_utilizing_headless_cms"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2624379000","690649307"]}